, 1345 , 1645 , 4536 , walking bass 個啲... 再變都係 modulation , relative 咁..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"前面都明，但modulation , relative係咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁定左個Chord，點落D Melody好<br />\n<br />\n例如1645 C Am F G<br />\n點作D Melody落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04642ce60a64bdacddaca855a3c791032d514cc6","tid":826900,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb36f342eede0d6a561a2534f8b86c41960d8f1","tid":826900,"uid":191246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:52:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"聽講MJ都係咁"},{"pid":"6eda9a5562d26aae8ac28ee4676825db5e4d9f06","tid":826900,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:35:44.000Z","msg":"練好聽力、熟用C major六個chord：<br />\nC，Dm，Em，F，G，Am<br />\n聽大量Cmajor既歌既chord progression<br />\n試用呢六個chord於每個bar配番主旋律<br />\n<br />\n之後再聽同用進階既chord<br />\n<br />\n配chord有對錯 但係可以多過一個answer<br />\n配配下自然識作"},{"pid":"6e9edb1967c6a2338e83e36f3ba0747f8b5b3a91","tid":826900,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"之後學第個key，將C major學識既chord progression轉移應用落第個key<br />\n<br />\n用數字排位方式理解chord progression<br />\n唔好死記chord 字母<br />\n因為數字排位係講緊一個chord<br />\n響當時既key既角色<br />\neg響C major key個F chord係四<br />\nA minor key 個F chord係六<br />\n同一個chord在唔同key係唔同數字排位<br />\n唔同chord在唔同key可以係同一個數字排位"},{"pid":"f92769bbc09d62f24b8d68aa1a06e989e5291fdd","tid":826900,"uid":210099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0a102eaf1b4f6a983c1c713d003b296dd531db","tid":826900,"uid":210099,"like":1,"dislike"